                            <comment id="15170130" author="daijy" created="Fri, 26 Feb 2016 23:48:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This happens while the scalar is null. The null scalar is a result of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4724&quot; title=&quot;GROUP ALL must create an output record in case there is no input&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-4724&quot;&gt;PIG-4724&lt;/a&gt;. As we don&apos;t have a good solution for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4724&quot; title=&quot;GROUP ALL must create an output record in case there is no input&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-4724&quot;&gt;PIG-4724&lt;/a&gt; yet, we shall allow null scalar value.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
